It was brought to our attention on July 6th, 2011 that the website www.5x5t.com has set up a subdomain called http://telcorock.5x5t.com/, where they have scraped our (Alden Systems) website code and added their own retail links at the top of the page.

We actually were made aware of the infringement via a google alert we had set up on Joint Use.
